      <title>挪威财富基金支持百事可乐生物多样性风险评估</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/land-use-biodiversity/norways-wealth-fund-backs-bid-pepsico-biodiversity-risk-assessment-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威主权财富基金计划支持一项股东提案，要求百事公司进行生物多样性风险评估，以衡量这家软饮料和零食巨头的业务对生物多样性丧失的脆弱性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/land-use-biodiversity/norways-wealth-fund-backs-bid-pepsico-biodiversity-risk-assessment-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 07:36:29 GMT</pubDate>
